    <main>
        <section class="page-section">
            <div class="container">

                <h1 class="section-title">Energy Saving Tips</h1>
                <p class="text-muted" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);">
                    Simple, renter-friendly tips to help reduce your electricity bills
                    without needing landlord approval.
                </p>

                <!-- SUMMARY CARDS -->
                <div class="card-grid" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);">
                    <div class="card" style="text-align: center;">
                        <h3>Total Potential Savings</h3>
                        <p style="font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: 4px;">
                            $1,062</p>
                        <span class="text-muted">per year</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card" style="text-align: center;">
                        <h3>Tips Available</h3>
                        <p style="font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: 4px;">8
                        </p>
                        <span class="text-muted">actionable items</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card" style="text-align: center;">
                        <h3>Quick Wins</h3>
                        <p style="font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: 4px;">6
                        </p>
                        <span class="text-muted">no-cost easy changes</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- 8 TIPS GRID -->
                <h2 class="section-title" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md);">All Tips</h2>
                <div class="card-grid" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);">

                    <div class="card">
                        <h3>Reduce Air Conditioning Usage</h3>
                        <p>Increase your AC temperature by 1–2 degrees and use fans first before turning on cooling.</p>
                        <p style="color: var(--color-primary); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);">Save
                            up to $320/year</p>
                        <a href="faq.html#quicktips" class="btn">Learn more</a>
                    </div>

                    <div class="card">
                        <h3>Run Pool Pump Off-Peak</h3>
                        <p>Schedule your pool pump to run during off-peak hours (before 3pm or after 9pm) to reduce
                            costs.</p>
                        <p style="color: var(--color-primary); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);">Save
                            up to $250/year</p>
                        <a href="faq.html#quicktips" class="btn">Learn more</a>
                    </div>

                    <div class="card">
                        <h3>Use Appliances During Daytime</h3>
                        <p>Run washing machines and dishwashers earlier in the day to avoid peak electricity rates.</p>
                        <p style="color: var(--color-primary); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);">Save
                            up to $180/year</p>
                        <a href="faq.html#quicktips" class="btn">Learn more</a>
                    </div>

                    <div class="card">
                        <h3>Turn Off Standby Devices</h3>
                        <p>Unplug unused electronics and switch off chargers, TVs, and consoles at the wall.</p>
                        <p style="color: var(--color-primary); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);">Save
                            up to $120/year</p>
                        <a href="faq.html#quicktips" class="btn">Learn more</a>
                    </div>

                    <div class="card">
                        <h3>Switch to LED Lighting</h3>
                        <p>Replace halogen or incandescent bulbs with LED alternatives — they use up to 75% less energy.
                        </p>
                        <p style="color: var(--color-primary); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);">Save
                            up to $100/year</p>
                        <a href="faq.html#quicktips" class="btn">Learn more</a>
                    </div>

                    <div class="card">
                        <h3>Wash Clothes in Cold Water</h3>
                        <p>Switching from hot to cold water for laundry reduces the energy used per wash by up to 90%.
                        </p>
                        <p style="color: var(--color-primary); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);">Save
                            up to $52/year</p>
                        <a href="faq.html#quicktips" class="btn">Learn more</a>
                    </div>

                    <div class="card">
                        <h3>Air Dry Clothes</h3>
                        <p>Dry clothes naturally on a rack or outdoor line instead of using a clothes dryer.</p>
                        <p style="color: var(--color-primary); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);">Save
                            up to $40/year</p>
                        <a href="faq.html#quicktips" class="btn">Learn more</a>
                    </div>

                    <div class="card">
                        <h3>Use Natural Light During the Day</h3>
                        <p>Open blinds and curtains during daylight hours before switching on artificial lights.</p>
                        <p style="color: var(--color-primary); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);">Save
                            up to $20/year</p>
                        <a href="faq.html#quicktips" class="btn">Learn more</a>
                    </div>

                </div>

                <!-- QUICK WINS SECTION — 6 no-cost changes -->
                <h2 class="section-title" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md);">Quick Wins — 6 Easy No-Cost Changes
                </h2>
                <div class="card">
                    <p class="text-muted" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md);">
                        These 6 actions cost nothing and can be done today.
                        Small habits can still make a difference over time.
                    </p>
                    <ul class="quick-wins-list">
                        <li>Turn off lights when leaving a room <span>— free</span></li>
                        <li>Use fans before turning on air conditioning <span>— free</span></li>
                        <li>Unplug phone chargers when not in use <span>— free</span></li>
                        <li>Run full loads in the washing machine <span>— free</span></li>
                        <li>Open curtains during the day to use natural light <span>— free</span></li>
                        <li>Switch off the TV at the wall instead of leaving it on standby <span>— free</span></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

            </div>
        </section>
